### Health check
GET http://localhost:5001/health

### Hot lead prediction
POST http://localhost:5001/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 32,
  "interactions": 8,
  "days_since_first": 14,
  "email_opens": 5,
  "demo_attended": true,
  "lead_score": 85,
  "source": "referral",
  "company_size": "enterprise"
}

